{"tid":1300313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［分析］歷史一直在重演 & 鬼 & 高官心態","createTime":"2019-07-09T10:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:48:37.000Z","uid":89627,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dac4101269c51971d5b775e3ec4eeede7f7e8b36","tid":1300313,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:34:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望大家花少少時間睇下</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.angelfire.com/hi/hayashi/64true13.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.angelfire.com%2Fhi%2Fhayashi%2F64true13.html&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=158fbc21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.angelfire.com/hi/hayashi/64true13.html</a><br />\n上面link係六四一事，我睇完覺得好似而家嘅香港，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 有人絕食，政府唔理。（金鐘陳伯）<br />\n<br />\n2. 軍人偽裝成平民進城 （52仔想返狗屋返工）<br />\n<br />\n3. 班高官搬弄是非，將鎮壓學生合理化 （612，旺角黑夜）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n三十年前，已經證明到班狗官係唔會care 大眾民意，佢哋只會諗住自己，所以唔好再旨意而家嘅政府會突然間良心發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望六四事件唔會再重演！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0abf11c17cc0560c0b1af78960a4ae1b9982f1","tid":1300313,"uid":89627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GRb4VY2dU4c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGRb4VY2dU4c&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=71415fa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GRb4VY2dU4c</a><br />\n呢條片經常被藍絲話「架坦克都冇碾過tank man ,中共如何屠殺平民」<br />\n<br />\n但其實細心睇吓推走tank man 嗰兩個黑衫人好可疑，疑似係鬼。（片尾show到佢示意叫坦克快啲行）"},{"pid":"cb9c828bc082cc3d0e76c72e812f9031100f5e5b","tid":1300313,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:38:07.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，